81,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T20:11:53.000Z","msg":"騙財好呀，同香港人講理想無人聽，親身體驗俾人呃錢就會少一堆民建聯鐵票"},{"pid":"169cf7cf4d6c5916354a0b2f4cc6e4013208ca24","tid":611181,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"292cce240db2d1883d39734dfdd653d15914713a","tid":611181,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"老嘢：政治嘅嘢我唔識"},{"pid":"a8721ecfbded5b3e57623a0a7905b74ad7bac36d","tid":611181,"uid":113512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:13:38.000Z","msg":"香港殺手行業人材短缺"},{"pid":"6748ac8a087c45166cdde16d83e435b238a0fc40","tid":611181,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:18:23.000Z","msg":"當年說我討厭政治，今日......"}]}